Hints for developers:

Adding a file to the project:
 - Create the files -- each class tends to get it's on .cpp and .h
 - Add the file to the list of SOURCES in Makefile.am
 - alterations to defines can be made in configure.in
 
Build preocedure is as follows
 - gmake -f Makefile.cvs
 - ./configure
 - gmake
 
